column2: SELECT so.specObjID, so.plate, so.mjd, so.FiberID, s.objID, s.ra, s.dec, s.g, s.r, sp.SPECTYPEHAMMER, FROM SpecObj AS so LEFT OUTER JOIN Star as s ON so.bestObjID = s.objID JOIN sppParams AS sp ON sp.specObjID = so.specObjID WHERE (so.ra between # and #) AND (so.dec between # and #) AND (s.g > #) and (s.g < #)
